cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper is about blind deblurring using deep neural networks. The most relevant sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), which deals with image processing and analysis. The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely sub-category as well. Additionally, the paper involves the use of generative and adversarial networks, which are commonly used in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) research. The paper also involves motion flow estimation, which is a topic in cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
